  splash-themes-livecd-2007.0-r2.ebuild:
  Switch to EAPI 2 and require splashutils to be installed with the 'png'
  USE flag.

  14 Sep 2008; Michał Januszewski <spock@gentoo.org>
  splash-themes-livecd-2004.3.ebuild, splash-themes-livecd-2005.0.ebuild,
